==Tamallayt==
Idurar n Djerdjer akk-d leǧwahi-nsen llan d aɣbalu n Turisme amqqran Γ ighrm n Tizi Wezzu imi yal usggas ilulufen n lɣaci temsafren ɣur-es iwakken ad sɛedin tizi n ustaɛfu-nsen; Taddart n Tala n yilef akk-d Tikejda d imukan i iɛejben aṭas n lɣaci deg tizi n Skii. 

Imukan n taɣedweft: 
Lwert Arumani: Tigzirt (Iomnium), Taqsebt (Rusupisir), Azzefun (Rosazu). Rrif n lebḥer (taftist) d ayen i ijebbden daɣen aṭas n middn di tamurt merra.

==Amzruy==
